{"tid":1536464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我屌哂你地班唔敢跳閘嘅人","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:03:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:14:18.000Z","uid":294427,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"18b334dc73c413c5e8e9b3bdd9f80a53c647c8e3","tid":1536464,"uid":294427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"屌你班人可唔可以有翻小小骨氣，係咪唔記得哂黨鐵封站搞到手足走唔到。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日屯門西鐵站都已經有手足直接開埋個緊急出口俾你地行，我見到幾個明明係自己友嘅但係到猶豫唔知應唔應該行過去好，諗諗下又係走過去拍卡入閘。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係屌哂你地班人，你地而家每俾一蚊黨鐵姐係支持緊佢地封站打9我地啲手足吖，跳閘唔係為左慳錢慳車費，而係要抗議要話俾黨鐵知 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我就係唔撚俾錢吖</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd7ab5b96d186872065e68516ee6d1b4bad555f","tid":1536464,"uid":134107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Gnbgry.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Gnbgry.jpg&h=076a76d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"4e5b590e7ef723f7d0d026e6d8fcf93e16ae5e95","tid":1536464,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:05:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"17c023e6fc0a99d8a6eeb4a6d0d9033758fe3ada","tid":1536464,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}